Cd1−xZnxS is another buffer layer which is promising as its bandgap can be varied between 2.42 eV (CdS) and 3.5 eV (ZnS). The bandgap of Cd1−xZnxS for different Zn composition (x) can be calculated using the following equation which is a modified Vegard’s law [15]:1EgCd1-xZnxS=2.566+0.041x+1.086x2eV.\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
